THE GAME
--------

  'Aye_Q' is a peg game played on a "cross" shaped board like
this:

                        o o o
                        o o o
                    o o o o o o o
                    o o o . o o o
                    o o o o o o o
                        o o o
                        o o o

  Gameplay is done by moving a peg to an empty space, but you can
only move a peg two spaces horizontally or vertically. Aye_Q
features two ways to play:

 -'Normal' play: You jump over a peg and it will be removed.

 -'Inverted' (backward) play: You jump over an empty space and a
                              peg will appear there.

  The goal of the game is to remove the pegs (or fill up the
board, if the game is "Inverted"), until only one peg is left
(or only one space is empty, in the "Inverted" game), preferably
in the center.

  Have fun!

